- Guys get bullied too.

40:56.955 --> 40:59.257
It's embarrassing to admit.

40:59.290 --> 41:00.926
It really sucks.

41:00.959 --> 41:03.862
But we're expected to just
ignore it.

41:03.895 --> 41:06.031
But it still hurts.

41:09.100 --> 41:13.739
- I thought that saying mean
stuff was just...

41:13.772 --> 41:15.874
joking around,

41:15.907 --> 41:17.676
being a guy,

41:17.709 --> 41:21.179
what you had to do to be cool.

41:21.212 --> 41:23.248
But...

41:23.281 --> 41:25.617
I was wrong.

41:25.651 --> 41:28.654
*

41:28.687 --> 41:31.089
- I didn't stand up for you.

41:31.122 --> 41:34.560
I didn't think I was
strong enough.

41:34.593 --> 41:37.162
I don't know if we could ever
be friends again,

41:37.195 --> 41:40.632
but I just want you to know

41:40.666 --> 41:42.801
I'm sorry.

